{"tid":746890,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"(說好的拋售美債?) 俄羅斯不在５月美債持倉名單上，中國日本續增持美債","createTime":"2018-07-18T03:06:27.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-18T04:49:28.000Z","uid":14918,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"4440be87528ad6e74351f683ad5865ccfb1a262b","tid":746890,"uid":14918,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-18T03:06:27.000Z","msg":"18/07/2018 10:44<br />\n《外地經濟》俄羅斯不在５月美債持倉名單上，中國日本續增持美債<br />\n<br />\n　　《經濟通通訊社１８日專訊》美國財政部公布，外國投資者５月買入美債，當中又以私人投資者為首，因在貿易及意大利政局動盪下，投資者尋求安全資產。　　<br />\n<br />\n不過俄羅斯５月已不在財政部的持倉名單中，先前數據顯示俄羅斯４月美債持倉已從３月的９６１億美元大幅降至４８７億美元。　　<br />\n<br />\n海外投資者５月買進２６６﹒９億美元的美債，４月及３月分別凈賣出４７﹒８億美元及４９﹒２億美元。當中私人投資者５月買入５０２﹒８億美元，抵消外國官方機構賣出的２３８億美元。　　<br />\n<br />\n中國及日本在５月均增持美債，中國的美債持倉量從４月的１﹒１８２萬億美元增至１﹒１８３萬億美元，日本則從１﹒０３１萬億美元增至１﹒０４９萬億美元。（ｍｎ）<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.etnet.com.hk/mobile/tc/news/categorized_news_detail.php?category=latest&amp;newsid=ETN280718237\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.etnet.com.hk%2Fmobile%2Ftc%2Fnews%2Fcategorized_news_detail.php%3Fcategory%3Dlatest%26newsid%3DETN280718237&d=S6G0BtnUd%2F2LN8rd4i%2FdHy7PofNJLCAwyGXsi6MH%2FEQ%3D&h=49e8d98d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.etnet.com.hk/mobile/tc/news/categorized_news_detail.php?category=latest&amp;newsid=ETN280718237</a>"},{"pid":"d3835c2c4db8c02b0d8035d8e6b9b88f8c31633d","tid":746890,"uid":47259,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-18T03:16:53.000Z","msg":"呢鋪俄佬咁有骨氣就抵讚喇, 反觀支那身體很誠實 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1543be14cc827e492ca9766cd9a13399932c8415","tid":746890,"uid":13503,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"d3835c2c4db8c02b0d8035d8e6b9b88f8c31633d","tid":746890,"uid":47259,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-18T03:16:53.000Z","msg":"呢鋪俄佬咁有骨氣就抵讚喇, 反觀支那身體很誠實 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-18T03:20:17.000Z","msg":"俄佬果幾百億相對美債萬億只係毛毛細雨，所以最大可能係俄佬經濟已經出現問題急需美金黎救濟<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/999.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4cf8188b9ed75ed375a452dd7123195f267d30f5","tid":746890,"uid":36390,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-18T03:21:23.000Z","msg":"民族大義，國家計劃去咗邊"},{"pid":"c01b1ca15c8614a8f926de15455b0d7e7d79a887","tid":746890,"uid":14918,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-18T03:34:35.000Z","msg":"2025"},{"pid":"024661fef20e72f725c3da1ebb6b58185cb57e6a","tid":746890,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-18T03:50:45.000Z","msg":"貿易戰真係完全無得打"},{"pid":"0588fd6c9a7017bff6211ddb2763f25835121e92","tid":746890,"uid":14918,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-18T04:49:28.000Z","msg":"不打了<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}